#: ../../docs/tutorials/physics/using_area_2d.rst:95
msgid "Areas are great for bullets and other projectiles that hit and deal damage, but don't need any other physics such as bouncing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/tutorials/physics/using_area_2d.rst:96
msgid "Use a large circular area around an enemy to define its \"detect\" radius. When the player is outside the area, the enemy can't \"see\" it."
msgstr ""

